    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cardeneer lets you engage in strategic, turn-based card battles. Explore various community-made card games or create your own with the editor. Make games, cards, abilities, and challenges to match your preferences, and design unique card layouts with your own artwork.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try out the different game modes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307260/extras/a46355b261f658b7c77d7512951fe2bd.poster.avif?t=1727974133\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307260/extras/a46355b261f658b7c77d7512951fe2bd.webm?t=1727974133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307260/extras/a46355b261f658b7c77d7512951fe2bd.mp4?t=1727974133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easily create your own games with the built-in editor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307260/extras/ce0119aeb81bab8f803e44c1dc5ce3a4.poster.avif?t=1727974133\" width=636 height=428 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307260/extras/ce0119aeb81bab8f803e44c1dc5ce3a4.webm?t=1727974133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307260/extras/ce0119aeb81bab8f803e44c1dc5ce3a4.mp4?t=1727974133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Craft unique special abilities using the ability editor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307260/extras/935f8c51df2503e627e9d27d34729b01.poster.avif?t=1727974133\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307260/extras/935f8c51df2503e627e9d27d34729b01.webm?t=1727974133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307260/extras/935f8c51df2503e627e9d27d34729b01.mp4?t=1727974133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Design the layout of your cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307260/extras/0f1e2fc13abeb621da47f23d05b062d7.poster.avif?t=1727974133\" width=600 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307260/extras/0f1e2fc13abeb621da47f23d05b062d7.webm?t=1727974133\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307260/extras/0f1e2fc13abeb621da47f23d05b062d7.mp4?t=1727974133\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307260/extras/1e1136349959de0eead7eb1f4caaeb60.webp?t=1727974133\" width=263 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
